com.qequipe.p11

Class LongRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.jna.PointerType
      • com.qequipe.p11.LongRef
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sun.jna.NativeMapped

    public class LongRef
extends com.sun.jna.PointerType
    JNA wrapper for ULONG. It is exactly like NativeLong except that I didn't like having JNA namespaces all through application code and I like typing 'val()' better than 'intValue()'.
    Author:
    Ugo Chirico - http://www.cyberneid.com
